Description:
In a dry oasis, you find an old man with the gear of a warrior, resting. He says he expects rain soon and suggests sharing stories while you wait.

It doesn’t seem like a bad idea, and when you mention that you are a group of adventurers on a mission, he smiles. He reveals that he was the best retiarius the Velkarath Colosseum ever knew, but now he is just an old and tired wanderer.

Age is taking its toll on him, but he may have something for young people like you: if you prove yourselves cunning fighters, he may give you a special arena badge to challenge Velkarath coliseum’s special trial.
DescriptionAction: Do you want the arena badge that he is offering?
